      • fromCharSource

        public static Source fromCharSource​(com.google.common.io.CharSource source)
        Create Source from a generic text source such as string, CharBuffer or text file. Useful when data is already in memory or can't be directly read from a file or url.
        Parameters:
        source - generic "re-redable" source of characters
        Returns:
        Source delegate for CharSource (can't be null)
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - when source is null
